{"id":126457,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":12,"day":12}],"page":"9","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"284","ytitle":"","mtitle":"血肉筵席","ftitle":"","authors":["任钧"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"任钧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要雇用几位名厨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我准备大大地请一次客。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为要讲究卫生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为要合乎时代潮流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从锅灶直到刀叉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我都要它们整个“机械化”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全副“美式配备”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，材料和做法呢?——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我却主张:“提倡国货”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实行“保存国粹”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的MeNu将是:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清燉灾民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红烧士兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活炒民主斗士心……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外加:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民汗血酸辣汤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤儿寡妇红泪酒……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就的客人自然不会是一些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脚牛屎的庄稼汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不会是一些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满身汗臭的苦力们；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(因为他们只配嚼青菜萝蔔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里够得上吃这些大鱼大肉!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是文官简任以上!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武官少将以上!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要加上大批的花旗贵宾!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为只有他们才有资格享受"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种“中国大菜”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能领略"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种“山珍海味”呵!……"}]}